%C3%A0nh-Ho%C3%A1-kh%C3%A2m-ph%C3%A1i-ch%C3%BA-th%E1%BB%91-Cam-L%E1%BB%99-t%E1%BA%A9u-b%C3%BAt-th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-bMJ2GVeXowLbdcTsk524Rw">Tiễn nguyên kinh doãn Nguyễn Văn Tường chi Thành Hoá khâm phái chú thố Cam Lộ tẩu bút thứ vận - 餞原京尹阮文祥之成化欽派注措甘露走筆次韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%B1-Nh%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C3%A2y-kinh-ph%C3%AC-th%E1%BA%A3-di-c%C6%B0-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%93n-mao-%E1%BB%91c-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-ClbrHgP42nFdMzPE56z2iQ">Tự Nhương Tây kinh phì thả di cư Đông Đồn mao ốc kỳ 4 - 自瀼西荊扉且移居東屯茅屋其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%E1%BB%AD-Th%C3%A0nh/U-c%C6%B0/poem-EDMv0UUW7NkrbVFcj2Vc7A">U cư - 幽居</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%E1%BB%AD-Th%C3%A0nh/author-HYGFT6wTz4aNfPlamWDBRw">Nguyễn Tử Thành</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kaneakirashin-no/%E1%BB%A8c-Quy-San-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-aQWagDyp9DBa7jEDnADpeg">Ức Quy San kỳ 2 - 憶龜山其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kaneakirashin-no/author-GogBEbTZG_IWXGiGCtg7Dw">Kaneakirashin&#039;no</a>)<br></div>	</div>
